Dia. 01 Eye vs. no eye
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's hane at 1 \cf1\b misses the good chance\cf0\b0 .
\par White blocks at 2 and wins the capturing race.
\par It became\cf2\b  eye vs. no eye\cf0\b0  situation.
\par Moreover Black 3 becomes gote.
\par
\par
\par }
