Dia. 02 Not Enough Liberties
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black 1 looks slightly better, but White 2 is the vital point of this capturing race.
\par
\par After the sequence from 3 to 6, Black doesn't have enough liberties and it is eye vs. no eye situation again.
\par
\par }
